{
  "texts": [
    "RS segmentation is a critical task in numerous real-world applications, including land cover mapping, urban planning, and environmental monitoring (He et al. 2022b).",
    "Cross-domain task is crucial due to the diversity of data, and lots of DA methods have been applied to improve the generalization ability of segmentation models (Rui and Jintao 2020; Tong et al. 2020).",
    "Compared with DA, the number of DG research (Iizuka, Xia, and Yokoya 2023; Liang et al. 2024) in RS is much less than DA.",
    "Although these works (Zhu et al. 2023) make contributions, most of them only focus on specialized models rather than leveraging the power of VFMs, leading to limited crossdomain capabilities.",
    "Vision Foundation ModelsVision Foundation Models (VFMs) have made significant progress and have exerted considerable influence across various AI-related fields."
  ]
}